def numberOfProposals() payable: 
  return (stor0 - 1)

def actualBalance() payable: 
  return (eth.balance(this.address) - stor13)

def divisor() payable: 
  if closingTime - (336 * 24 * 3600) > block.timestamp:
      return 20
  if closingTime - (96 * 24 * 3600) <= block.timestamp:
      return 30
  return ((block.timestamp + -closingTime + (336 * 24 * 3600) / 24 * 3600) + 20)

def approve(address _spender, uint256 _value) payable: 
  allowance[caller][addr(_spender)] = _value
  log Approval(
        address tokenOwner=_value,
        address spender=caller,
        uint256 tokens=_spender)
  return 1

def changeProposalDeposit(uint256 _proposalDeposit) payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  require caller == this.address
  require _proposalDeposit <= eth.balance(this.address) - stor13 + rewardToken[addr(this.address)] / 100
  proposalDeposit = _proposalDeposit

def unblockMe() payable: 
  if blocked[caller]:
      require blocked[caller] < stor0
      if block.timestamp <= uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * stor11[caller]) + 3].field_0):
          return 1
      blocked[caller] = 0
      return 0
  else:
      return 0

def checkProposalCode(uint256 _proposalNumber, address _beneficiary, uint256 _amount, bytes _transactionBytecode) payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  require _proposalNumber < stor0
  return (uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalNumber) + 5].field_0) == sha3(_beneficiary, _amount, _transactionBytecode[all]))

def halveMinQuorum() payable: 
  if stor2.length >= block.timestamp - (4200 * 24 * 3600):
      if addr(newDAO.length) != caller:
          return 0
  if stor2.length >= block.timestamp - (336 * 24 * 3600):
      return 0
  stor2.length = block.timestamp
  bool(stor1.length) = 0
  uint255(stor1.length.field_1) = uint255(stor1.length)
  return 1

def changeAllowedRecipients(address _recipient, bool _allowed) payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  require caller == addr(newDAO.length)
  uint256(allowedRecipients[addr(_recipient)]) = _allowed or Mask(248, 8, uint256(allowedRecipients[addr(_recipient)]))
  log AllowedRecipientChanged(
        address recipient=_allowed,
        bool allowed=_recipient)
  return 1

def newContract(address _newContract) payable: 
  if caller == this.address:
      if uint8(allowedRecipients[addr(_newContract)]):
          call _newContract with:
             value eth.balance(this.address) wei
               gas gas_remaining - 34050 wei
          require ext_call.success
          rewardToken[_newContract] += rewardToken[addr(this.address)]
          rewardToken[addr(this.address)] = 0
          dAOpaidOut[_newContract] += dAOpaidOut[addr(this.address)]
          dAOpaidOut[addr(this.address)] = 0

def getMyReward() payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  call rewardAccount.accumulatedInput() with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
  require ext_call.success
  require balanceOf[caller] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalSupply >= paidOut[caller]
  call rewardAccount.accumulatedInput() with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
  require ext_call.success
  call rewardAccount.payOut(address recipient, uint256 amount) with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
      args caller, (balanceOf[caller] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalSupply) - paidOut[caller]
  require ext_call.return_data[0]
  paidOut[caller] = balanceOf[caller] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalSupply
  return 1

def transfer(address _to, uint256 _value) payable: 
  require isFueled
  require block.timestamp > closingTime
  if blocked[caller]:
      require blocked[caller] < stor0
      require block.timestamp > uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * stor11[caller]) + 3].field_0)
      blocked[caller] = 0
  require _value * paidOut[caller] / balanceOf[caller] <= paidOut[caller]
  paidOut[caller] -= _value * paidOut[caller] / balanceOf[caller]
  paidOut[_to] += _value * paidOut[caller] / balanceOf[caller]
  require call.value <= 0
  require balanceOf[caller] >= _value
  require _value > 0
  balanceOf[caller] -= _value
  balanceOf[_to] += _value
  log Transfer(
        address from=_value,
        address to=caller,
        uint256 tokens=_to)
  return 1

def retrieveDAOReward(bool _toMembers) payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  call dAOrewardAccount.accumulatedInput() with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
  require ext_call.success
  require rewardToken[caller] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalRewardToken >= dAOpaidOut[caller]
  call dAOrewardAccount.accumulatedInput() with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
  require ext_call.success
  if not _toMembers:
      call dAOrewardAccount.payOut(address recipient, uint256 amount) with:
           gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
          args caller, (rewardToken[caller] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalRewardToken) - dAOpaidOut[caller]
      require ext_call.success
  else:
      call caller.rewardAccount() with:
           gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
      require ext_call.success
      call dAOrewardAccount.payOut(address recipient, uint256 amount) with:
           gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
          args addr(ext_call.return_data[0]), (rewardToken[caller] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalRewardToken) - dAOpaidOut[caller]
  require ext_call.return_data[0]
  dAOpaidOut[caller] = rewardToken[caller] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalRewardToken
  return 1

def refund() payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  if block.timestamp > closingTime:
      if not isFueled:
          call extraBalanceAddress.accumulatedInput() with:
               gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
          require ext_call.success
          if eth.balance(extraBalanceAddress) < ext_call.return_data[0]:
              call caller with:
                 value stor19[caller] wei
                   gas gas_remaining - 34050 wei
              if ext_call.success:
                  log Refund(
                        address investor=stor19[caller],
                        uint256 weiAmount=caller)
                  totalSupply -= balanceOf[caller]
                  balanceOf[caller] = 0
                  stor19[caller] = 0
          else:
              call extraBalanceAddress.accumulatedInput() with:
                   gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
              require ext_call.success
              call extraBalanceAddress.payOut(address recipient, uint256 amount) with:
                   gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
                  args addr(this.address), ext_call.return_data[0]
              call caller with:
                 value stor19[caller] wei
                   gas gas_remaining - 34050 wei
              log Refund(
                    address investor=stor19[caller],
                    uint256 weiAmount=caller)
              totalSupply -= balanceOf[caller]
              balanceOf[caller] = 0
              stor19[caller] = 0

def vote(uint256 _proposalID, bool _supportsProposal) payable: 
  require balanceOf[caller]
  require call.value <= 0
  require _proposalID < stor0
  require not uint8(stor[(14 * _proposalID) + 0x290decd9548b62a8d60345a988386fc84ba6bc95484008f6362f93160ef3e56e][caller].field_0)
  require not uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 12][caller].field_0)
  require block.timestamp < uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 3].field_0)
  if not _supportsProposal:
      uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 10].field_0) += balanceOf[caller]
      uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 12][caller].field_0) = 1
  else:
      uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 9].field_0) += balanceOf[caller]
      uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 11][caller].field_0) = 1
  if not blocked[caller]:
      blocked[caller] = _proposalID
  else:
      require blocked[caller] < stor0
      if uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 3].field_0) > stor290D[stor11[caller]]:
          blocked[caller] = _proposalID
  log Voted(
        uint256 proposalID=_supportsProposal,
        bool position=_proposalID,
        address voter=caller)
  return 0

def transferFrom(address _from, address _to, uint256 _value) payable: 
  require isFueled
  require block.timestamp > closingTime
  if blocked[addr(_from)]:
      require blocked[addr(_from)] < stor0
      require block.timestamp > uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * stor11[addr(_from)]) + 3].field_0)
      blocked[addr(_from)] = 0
  require _value * paidOut[addr(_from)] / balanceOf[addr(_from)] <= paidOut[addr(_from)]
  paidOut[addr(_from)] -= _value * paidOut[addr(_from)] / balanceOf[addr(_from)]
  paidOut[_to] += _value * paidOut[addr(_from)] / balanceOf[addr(_from)]
  require call.value <= 0
  require balanceOf[addr(_from)] >= _value
  require allowance[addr(_from)][caller] >= _value
  require _value > 0
  balanceOf[addr(_to)] += _value
  balanceOf[_from] -= _value
  allowance[addr(_from)][caller] -= _value
  log Transfer(
        address from=_value,
        address to=_from,
        uint256 tokens=_to)
  return 1

def proposals(uint256 _param1) payable: 
  require _param1 < stor0
  mem[512] = uint256(stor[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 2)].field_0)
  idx = 512
  s = 0
  while stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 2].length + 512 > idx + 32:
      mem[idx + 32] = uint256(stor[s + sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 2) + 1].field_0)
      idx = idx + 32
      s = s + 1
      continue 
  return addr(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1)].field_0), 
         uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 1].field_0),
         Array(len=stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 2].length, data=mem[512 len stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 2].length + (floor32(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 2].length - 1) + -stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 2].length + 32 % 32)]),
         uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 3].field_0),
         uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 4].field_0),
         uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 4].field_0),
         uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 5].field_0),
         uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 6].field_0),
         uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 7].field_0),
         uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 9].field_0),
         uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 10].field_0),
         addr(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _param1) + 13].field_0)

def createTokenProxy(address _tokenHolder) payable: 
  require block.timestamp < closingTime
  require call.value > 0
  if privateCreationAddress:
      require caller == privateCreationAddress
  if closingTime - (336 * 24 * 3600) > block.timestamp:
      call extraBalanceAddress with:
         value call.value - (20 * call.value / 20) wei
           gas gas_remaining - 34050 wei
      balanceOf[addr(_tokenHolder)] += 20 * call.value / 20
      totalSupply += 20 * call.value / 20
      stor19[addr(_tokenHolder)] += call.value
      log CreatedToken(
            address to=(20 * call.value / 20),
            uint256 amount=_tokenHolder)
      if totalSupply >= minTokensToCreate:
          if not isFueled:
              isFueled = 1
              log FuelingToDate(uint256 value=totalSupply)
  else:
      if closingTime - (96 * 24 * 3600) <= block.timestamp:
          call extraBalanceAddress with:
             value call.value - (20 * call.value / 30) wei
               gas gas_remaining - 34050 wei
          balanceOf[addr(_tokenHolder)] += 20 * call.value / 30
          totalSupply += 20 * call.value / 30
          stor19[addr(_tokenHolder)] += call.value
          log CreatedToken(
                address to=(20 * call.value / 30),
                uint256 amount=_tokenHolder)
      else:
          call extraBalanceAddress with:
             value call.value - (20 * call.value / (block.timestamp + -closingTime + (336 * 24 * 3600) / 24 * 3600) + 20) wei
               gas gas_remaining - 34050 wei
          balanceOf[addr(_tokenHolder)] += 20 * call.value / (block.timestamp + -closingTime + (336 * 24 * 3600) / 24 * 3600) + 20
          totalSupply += 20 * call.value / (block.timestamp + -closingTime + (336 * 24 * 3600) / 24 * 3600) + 20
          stor19[addr(_tokenHolder)] += call.value
          log CreatedToken(
                address to=(20 * call.value / (block.timestamp + -closingTime + (336 * 24 * 3600) / 24 * 3600) + 20),
                uint256 amount=_tokenHolder)
      if totalSupply >= minTokensToCreate:
          if not isFueled:
              isFueled = 1
              log FuelingToDate(uint256 value=totalSupply)
  return 1

                  balanceOf[caller] += 20 * call.value / (block.timestamp + -closingTime + (336 * 24 * 3600) / 24 * 3600) + 20

def transferFromWithoutReward(address _from, address _to, uint256 _value) payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  call rewardAccount.accumulatedInput() with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
  require ext_call.success
  require balanceOf[addr(_from)] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalSupply >= paidOut[addr(_from)]
  call rewardAccount.accumulatedInput() with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
  require ext_call.success
  call rewardAccount.payOut(address recipient, uint256 amount) with:
       gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
      args addr(_from), (balanceOf[addr(_from)] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalSupply) - paidOut[addr(_from)]
  require ext_call.return_data[0]
  paidOut[addr(_from)] = balanceOf[addr(_from)] * ext_call.return_data[0] / totalSupply
  require isFueled
  require block.timestamp > closingTime
  if blocked[addr(_from)]:
      require blocked[addr(_from)] < stor0
      require block.timestamp > uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * stor11[addr(_from)]) + 3].field_0)
      blocked[addr(_from)] = 0
  require _value * paidOut[addr(_from)] / balanceOf[addr(_from)] <= paidOut[addr(_from)]
  paidOut[addr(_from)] -= _value * paidOut[addr(_from)] / balanceOf[addr(_from)]
  paidOut[_to] += _value * paidOut[addr(_from)] / balanceOf[addr(_from)]
  require call.value <= 0
  require balanceOf[addr(_from)] >= _value
  require allowance[addr(_from)][caller] >= _value
  require _value > 0
  balanceOf[addr(_to)] += _value
  balanceOf[_from] -= _value
  allowance[addr(_from)][caller] -= _value
  log Transfer(
        address from=_value,
        address to=_from,
        uint256 tokens=_to)
  return 1

def splitDAO(uint256 _proposalID, address _newCurator) payable: 
  require call.value <= 0
  require balanceOf[caller]
  require _proposalID < stor0
  require block.timestamp >= stor290D[_proposalID]
  require block.timestamp <= uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 3].field_0) + (648 * 24 * 3600)
  require _newCurator == addr(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID)].field_0)
  require uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 7].field_0)
  require uint8(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 11][caller].field_0)
  if _proposalID != blocked[caller]:
      require not blocked[caller]
  require 0 < uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8].field_0)
  if addr(newDAO[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8)]):
      require 0 < uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8].field_0)
  else:
      log NewCurator(address newCurator=_newCurator)
      call daoCreatorAddress.0xe2faf044 with:
           gas gas_remaining - 25050 wei
          args 0, 0, 0, 0, block.timestamp + (648 * 24 * 3600)
      require ext_call.success
      require 0 < uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8].field_0)
      uint256(newDAO[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8)]) = ext_call.return_data[0] or Mask(96, 160, uint256(newDAO[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8)]))
      require addr(newDAO[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8)])
      require eth.balance(this.address) >= stor13
      require 0 < uint256(stor[code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8].field_0)
      uint256(stor[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8)].field_0) = eth.balance(this.address) - stor13
      stor2[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8)] = rewardToken[addr(this.address)]
      uint256(stor1[sha3(code.data[10806 len 32] + (14 * _proposalID) + 8)].field_0) = totalSupply
